    "faq": {
      "type": "faq",
      "blocks": {
        "question-4": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "<strong>Does Saturn comes with a rear rack and fenders?</strong>",
            "text": "<p>Yes. The rear fender comes pre-installed. The <strong>front fender</strong> and <strong>rear rack</strong> are included in the box and requires installation.</p>",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "question-1": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "<strong>How to set Saturn to Class 2 or Class 3? Can I customize the speed for each PAS level?</strong>",
            "text": "<p>You can adjust the riding speed and classes in <strong>two ways</strong>:</p><p><strong>- Via the Heybike app</strong><br/>Speed settings for PAS and throttle can be adjusted under Personalize → Speed Settings.<br/><br/><strong>- Via the display settings</strong><br/>On the display, the change can be made through manual adjustment of top speed.</p>",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "question-2": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "<strong>What is the warranty for Saturn?</strong>",
            "text": "<p>Saturn purchased from our official website comes with a 2-year limited warranty. For full details, <a href=\"/pages/warranty\" title=\"Warranty\">visit our Warranty page. </a></p>",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "question-3": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "<strong>Where can I find the Saturn manual and video assembly instruction?</strong>",
            "text": "<p>A user manual card is included in the product package. Scan the QR code on the card to access our <a href=\"https://heybike.nextop.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://heybike.nextop.com/\">user manual page</a>. You can also download from here. </p>",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        }
      },
